data.description: Welcome to the heart of Haymount! This Cape Cod style home is located on a cul-de-sac and offers all the charm of the historic Haymount community. The first floor offers 2 bedrooms and a bath, large living space with gas fireplace, formal dining room with built in cabinets/buffet, kitchen with updated appliances and granite countertops, and large laundry room! The second floor also has 2 bedrooms and 1 bath and loft space. The fenced in backyard has a lovely brick patio, perfect for entertaining.
